These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-2-1::.
There are 3 different nationalities: dutch, malaysian, turkish
1. the turkish is on the left of the malaysian##1
2. the turkish is between the dutch and the malaysian##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |  2   |    3     |
| Nationality   | dutch | turkish | malaysian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-2-2::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: epic, family, thriller
1. the person watching epic movies is between the person watching family movies and the person watching thriller movies##2
2. the person watching family movies is on the right of the person watching epic movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |   3    |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller | epic | family |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-2-3::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: electronic, indie, trance
1. the fan of indie is between the fan of electronic and the fan of trance##2
2. the fan of indie is on the left of the fan of electronic##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |  2   |    3    |
| Music-Genre   | trance | indie | electronic |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-2-4::.
3 different pets are kept: rat, turtle, goldfish
1. the owner of the goldfish is on the left of the owner of the turtle##1
2. the owner of the goldfish is between the owner of the turtle and the owner of the rat##2

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1    |   2   |     3      |
| Pet   | rat | goldfish | turtle |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-2-5::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, fanta, tea
1. the person drinking iced-tea is between the person drinking tea and the person drinking fanta##2
2. the person drinking tea is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |  2   |  3   |
| Beverage   | fanta | iced-tea | tea |

 #################################

 
